{"tid":1285932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學老師因反送中面書言論被捕！曾焯文報導","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T01:32:49.000Z","uid":201031,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f32ba5e74483c52e53706d214252dd061546f92d","tid":1285932,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"香港小學教師梁慧敏今日接受本報訪問，表示昨日（七月二號）被警察拘捕，罪名係「 威脅會摧毀或損壞財產  」， 所謂證據乃係梁慧敏曾在面書發表反送中等言論，例如「講咁多仲乜？下週立法會放雞尾酒啦！屌！ 」換言之，香港警方可以隨時以網言入人罪，違反言論自由。警方今日下晝開記招，透露經捕拘六男二女，年齡介乎十六歲至四十歲，涉網上公開警員資料、不誠實取用電腦及刑事損壞等行為，其中即包括梁慧敏。<br />\n警方昨日申請到搜查令，徹底搜查梁慧敏家，並且拍低大量私人空間照片，令其家人十分激動。<br />\n在差館落口供期間，警察曾向梁慧敏展示梁自己的面書頭像照片，其上印有「反修例 撤惡法」及「初一義士無罪」字句，問其有何政治目的？ 是否分享過涂謹申議員直播立法會審議逃犯條例的貼文？及貼文中「雞尾酒」何解？是否認識曾 like 或 share有關帖文的人？梁慧敏堅決行使保持箴默的權利。梁現已保釋，須於八月返差館報到，等睇律政會否起訴。<br />\n <br />\n#LeungWaiman #freedomofspeech #hongkongpolice #ccp #extraditionlaw #hongkongextraditionlaw #donaldtrump #maga2020 #keepamericagreat #chapmanchen #HKBNews #hongkongfreedomofspeech #hongkonghumanrights #反送中　#引渡條例　#逃犯條例　#香港言論自由　#曾焯文　#chapmanchen <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongbilingualnews.com/post/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%81%E6%9B%BE%E7%84%AF%E6%96%87%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E?fbclid=IwAR1nXGDcPub90A-L7EexSxA81pf56UKw1vs4w_nN6NWDuUllCstv2BptAKY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongbilingualnews.com%2Fpost%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2584%25AF%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1nXGDcPub90A-L7EexSxA81pf56UKw1vs4w_nN6NWDuUllCstv2BptAKY&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=2d634b1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongbilingualnews.com/post/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%81%E6%9B%BE%E7%84%AF%E6%96%87%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E?fbclid=IwAR1nXGDcPub90A-L7EexSxA81pf56UKw1vs4w_nN6NWDuUllCstv2BptAKY</a>"},{"pid":"3cf281724817ae107dabaa0cea3637ae35e43159","tid":1285932,"uid":259700,"like":1,"dislike":111,"score":-110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b26f7aad0b79a9f420ca1f0664e77f54b301c224","tid":1285932,"uid":2772,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"3cf281724817ae107dabaa0cea3637ae35e43159","tid":1285932,"uid":259700,"like":1,"dislike":111,"score":-110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:32:14.000Z","msg":"甩p先好學人帶風向喇支那賤種"},{"pid":"642bba7787be3490a90afdae753cd768d0b87677","tid":1285932,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149c7f7342beca0785cbc68af0bfcac61dc9a65c","tid":1285932,"uid":133340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"梁慧敏堅決行使保持箴默的權利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞尾酒，飲既唔得咩？<br />\non9警犬想玩白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搜屋應對需知：<br />\n<br />\n（1）當警察要搜查處所，他們必須出示有效的搜查令，請務必檢查清楚搜查令是否有效：<br />\n- 必須有正確的被搜者名字（你的名字）<br />\n- 搜查令賦權搜查的地方（警只可搜該範圍）<br />\n- 懷疑已經或即將或意圖犯的罪行<br />\n- 搜查令下可檢取的物品<br />\n- 搜查令的有效期<br />\n- 裁判法院蓋印及裁判官簽署<br />\n（2）你有權要求有律師在場時先才開始進行搜查<br />\n（3）如需律師援助，請即聯絡請求協助<br />\n（4）你有權拍攝整個搜查過程<br />\n（5）未有列在搜查令入面的物品，你有權拒絕交給警察<br />\n（6）如果搜查令無包括搜查電腦電話內的資料，你可以拒絕解鎖<br />\n（7）搜查後可要求警察提供檢取物品列表副本<br />\n<br />\n有冇做齊呀屌你"},{"pid":"a39fa793ce6265f075e336dbf7436db22bb3fbf3","tid":1285932,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家想嚇大家，想捉邊嗰任佢砌。"},{"pid":"e012ea5555c05d4df9d1f094b742961319a60dfa","tid":1285932,"uid":15880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"睇下你幾時搞錯藍絲<br />\n佢地刑事括免權, 公安睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480dd6b6d07b1c3005ba4777b4bee03d64ddfb44","tid":1285932,"uid":42521,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:37:52.000Z","msg":"警務處處長曾偉雄，今日被記者問到警方會否主動調查，行政長官梁振英的女兒梁齊昕懷疑遭遇家暴的事件，曾偉雄回應稱，不是在網上說過的事情，警方就要調查：<br />\n「網上有好多嘢發生，有好多言論，不能就有關人士喺網上講過乜就去調查。就等於你喺網上講嘅嘢，都唔希望警方調查，係咪？」"},{"pid":"44f6b7cd6c19473e68540b7748f1630b708210aa","tid":1285932,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T00:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2424345ddc1ddc02009970f28bf35d79918e1056","tid":1285932,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3cf281724817ae107dabaa0cea3637ae35e43159","tid":1285932,"uid":259700,"like":1,"dislike":111,"score":-110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T00:26:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n請問你唔識野(會員#259700)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286365\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286365</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"a6a7cd804d1e04328ba7bec7dfd48eee645d9ec8","tid":1285932,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T00:31:22.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中五大訴求</span><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"p